  "text": "As suggested by [CITATION_1] , successful community networks are likely to be acquired by major providers -for example, Reggefiber is now the majority stakeholder of OnsNet [CITATION_2] . On the other hand, initiatives like Guifi.net remain independent, thereby proving that community networks can develop without being incorporated by commercial operators.",
